n經濟生產力就變左創意，創作之類。"},{"pid":"226ed16e52e38a3cbb300b3ea36af03125cb15a6","tid":310540,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未來世界, 人類根本是多餘的</blockquote><br />\n可能係窮人，低智商的人係多餘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c459c4a687d5503529cef8c525b5ce1ac51550f","tid":310540,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當AI取代大量工作時<br />\n大部份人靠咩生存?<br />\n大部份人冇野做冇糧出冇錢買野時<br />\n經濟會點行?</blockquote><br />\n其實錢只係政府希望人去勞動生產，從而得到物質的媒介。<br />\n<br />\n但假如機械人已經可以生產所有人的物質及需求，錢其實都冇意義，人去工作亦都冇必要。<br />\n<br />\n經濟生產力就變左創意，創作之類。</blockquote><br />\n你係有錢佬會唔會畀呢件事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302725d8ff82a3fc7471cc8161b3fd0cf4c95ca4","tid":310540,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當AI取代大量工作時<br />\n大部份人靠咩生存?<br />\n大部份人冇野做冇糧出冇錢買野時<br />\n經濟會點行?</blockquote><br />\n其實錢只係政府希望人去勞動生產，從而得到物質的媒介。<br />\n<br />\n但假如機械人已經可以生產所有人的物質及需求，錢其實都冇意義，人去工作亦都冇必要。<br />\n<br />\n經濟生產力就變左創意，創作之類。</blockquote><br />\n咁樣一個獨栽政府根本無誘因去保障國家人口"},{"pid":"9e7b3e8b59f677e27945ac52d71040b1e29a6c18","tid":310540,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>linux 取代 windows</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd22508a44a67863437013e835d39116d8b71b7","tid":310540,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"除非解決到就業同生活問題, 如果唔係政府一定唔會比件事發生"},{"pid":"90728d4ef27324b93a1e2d58