大部份人冇野做冇糧出冇錢買野時<br />\n經濟會點行?</blockquote><br />\n其實錢只係政府希望人去勞動生產，從而得到物質的媒介。<br />\n<br />\n但假如機械人已經可以生產所有人的物質及需求，錢其實都冇意義，人去工作亦都冇必要。<br />\n<br />\n經濟生產力就變左創意，創作之類。</blockquote><br />\n你係有錢佬會唔會畀呢件事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係掌權者想唔想"},{"pid":"0f5f3803dffed9875c0f640864cc988743c1fc93","tid":310540,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:01:03.000Z","msg":"又唔記得2001太空漫遊同回到未來嘅教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88f40b8257946852bd5562a482514d8ff8e716f","tid":310540,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當AI取代大量工作時<br />\n大部份人靠咩生存?<br />\n大部份人冇野做冇糧出冇錢買野時<br />\n經濟會點行?</blockquote><br />\n機器人大量進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 糧食、消費品平左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我唔會等到"},{"pid":"791c62078cf3de3556de58bea9d286389169bb9f","tid":310540,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"聽住先，全民IT狗"},{"pid":"de7cbf6f442aae786509ca8c95ddcb63a268ffa6","tid":310540,"uid":74484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"之前聽人講未來只會有三類職業：工程師，演員，售後服務"},{"pid":"101405c605bebd83631cf9ec43eb7cadae3720b9","tid":310540,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"我地係咪活係另一個平行世界？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7407a281476b3cf0057ce53ac413447c7dcec3","tid":310540,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"人人用bitcoin時，retail bank應該會死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3da3d1ac285b4fd79cbe3329a43f2b4d526fa7f","tid":310540,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:18:53